                <baseMoodEffect>3</baseMoodEffect>
            </li>
            <li>
                <label>reverted</label>
                <description>Damnit. I enjoyed being able to topple buildings with my breath.</description>
                <baseMoodEffect>-3</baseMoodEffect>
            </li>
            <li>
                <label>reverted</label>
                <description>No more metal skin, no more giant wings, just my usual self. This is a tremendous relief.</description>
